## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="11bf4-109"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> 环境事务时可能会挂起和<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Complete%2A>称为并且之后事务被回滚。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11bf4-109"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> may hang when there is an ambient transaction and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Complete%2A> is called and afterwards the transaction is rolled back.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11bf4-110">如果<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A>调用在完成事务回滚之前, 的争用条件将存在，导致对的调用<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A>挂起。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11bf4-110">If <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> is called prior to the transaction rollback completing, a race condition will exist, causing the call to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> to hang.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11bf4-111">这可以通过下面的伪代码示例说明</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11bf4-111">This can be illustrated by the following pseudo-code example</span></span>  
  
```  
using (TransactionScope ts = new TransactionScope())   
{  
   try  
   {  
       rc.Complete();  
      ...  
   }  
   Catch (Exception)   
   {  
      rc.Abandon()  
   }  
}  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="11bf4-112">这不是用于处理 T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.RecieveContext 建议的模式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11bf4-112">This is not the recommended pattern for working with T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.RecieveContext.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11bf4-113">而是 try/catch 块应放置在事务范围之外。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11bf4-113">Instead the try/catch block should be placed outside of the transaction scope.</span></span>

